(AIR-RAID SIREN WAILING)

76
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,691
(PANICKED YELLING)

77
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,644
Everyone,
down to the shelters!

78
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,205
In chaos is death!

79
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,803
(DOOR CREAKING)

80
