191
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,401
Goodbye, Peter!

192
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,081
(PETER GRUNTS)

193
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,006
- You're comin' with me!
-Let go!

194
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,401
(PETER SCREAMING)

195
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,809
