202
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:57,726
<i>NIBS: We have to!</i>

203
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:59,126
Come on!

204
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:01,001
Nibs!

205
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,645
(SCREAMING)

206
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:06,009
And away we go!

207
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,571
